OL,3,CShots fired at property in east Belfast
OL,5,FPolice are investigating after shots
OL,6,Fwere fired at a house in east Belfast.
OL,8,FThe incident was reported on Wednesday
OL,9,Fat 8.30pm in the Tamery Pass area of
OL,10,Fthe city.
OL,12,FNobody was present at the property and
OL,13,Fno injuries were reported.
OL,15,FThe incident caused damage to the
OL,16,Ffront and rear windows.
OL,18,FPolice are working to establish a
OL,19,Fmotive for the attack.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/2
